cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.NA, cs.GR 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image registration and alignment. It may also belong to the machine learning (cs.MM) and learning (cs.LG) sub-categories as it involves the use of optimization and regularization techniques. The numerical analysis (cs.NA) sub-category is also a possibility as it involves solving a linear system. Finally, the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category may be relevant as the paper deals with electron microscopy image datasets.
